OL,3,CThe 'arrogant' headteacher who
OL,4,Csexually preyed on teenage girls
OL,6,FHe posed as a decent and caring head
OL,7,Fteacher. In reality, was a child
OL,8,Fabuser, preying on teenage girls.
OL,10,FFoden started teaching in 1979, and
OL,11,Fnow more than four decades later his
OL,12,Freputation is in tatters as he awaits
OL,13,Fa prison sentence, found guilty of
OL,14,Fserious sexual crimes against
OL,15,Fteenagers.
OL,17,FFor four years he sexually abused four
OL,18,Fgirls, urging them to keep quiet about
OL,19,Fwhat he was doing, even telling one
OL,20,Fshe "must take it to the grave and not
OL,21,Ftell anyone".
