OL,3,CThe 'arrogant' headteacher who
OL,4,Csexually preyed on teenage girls
OL,6,FFor more than three weeks, the former
OL,7,FGywnedd headteacher sat inside court
OL,8,Froom number one of Mold Crown Court
OL,9,Fand listened to the allegations five
OL,10,Fgirls had made against him. He was
OL,11,Ffound guilty of 19 charges, including
OL,12,F12 of sexual activity with a child
OL,13,Frelating to four girls. He was found
OL,14,Fnot guilty of the same charge in
OL,15,Frelation to a fifth girl.
OL,17,FHe was a member of the community in
OL,18,Fnorth-west Wales who was held in high
OL,19,Fregard by many, but he is now facing a
OL,20,Flengthy custodial sentence for his
OL,21,Fcrimes.
