OL,3,CThe 'arrogant' headteacher who
OL,4,Csexually preyed on teenage girls
OL,6,FHe said he had shown himself to be
OL,7,F"arrogant" with a "controlling
OL,8,Fpersonality" and an "individual used
OL,9,Fto getting his own way".
OL,11,FHe added: "This defendant was arrogant
OL,12,Fand couldn't care less. He was Neil
OL,13,FFoden, a man in his view who could do
OL,14,Fno wrong."
OL,16,FFoden, 66, of Old Colwyn, was arrested
OL,17,Fin September last year when plain-
OL,18,Fclothed officers went to his place of
OL,19,Fwork.
