OL,4,Csexually preyed on teenage girls
OL,6,FOn that autumn day, just 45 minutes
OL,7,Fbefore his arrest he deleted 17 images
OL,8,Fsent to him by one of the victims.
OL,9,FThere were photographs and videos,
OL,10,Fsome of which were of a sexual nature.
OL,11,FThey had been stored in a secret
OL,12,Ffolder protected by a password.
OL,14,FHe was taken to Caernarfon police
OL,15,Fstation for questioning - answering
OL,16,F"no comment" to everything put to him.
OL,18,FHis arrest came after a complaint from
OL,19,Fa teenager - known as Child A.
